flowchart TB
  C[Client]
  C --> E[Entry: firm page or firm-designated lead]
  E --> REQ[Connection / onboard request]
  REQ --> FA[Firm accepts]
  FA --> MAT[Matter under firm]
  MAT --> ASG[Firm assigns lead advocate]
  ASG --> UI[Client sees: firm identity plus matter lead]
  ASG --> CH[Firm may reassign advocate on matter]
  CH --> UI
